  <summary date="2021-05-10T14:34:49Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop Online Ammunition Sales Act of 2021

This bill establishes new requirements and restrictions with respect to the sale, purchase, shipment, and transport of ammunition.

Among other things, the bill

 requires an ammunition dealer to be licensed; requires ammunition sales to be conducted in person; and requires a licensed ammunition importer, manufacturer, or dealer to report on bulk sales of ammunition.</summary>
